  <brief_title>INvestigation on Routine Follow-up in CONgestive HearT FAilure Patients With Remotely Monitored Implanted Cardioverter Defibrillators (ICD) SysTems</brief_title>
  <acronym>InContact</acronym>
  <official_title>INvestigation on Routine Follow-up in CONgestive HearT FAilure Patients With Remotely Monitored ICD SysTems</official_title>
